snippet.textDisplay: A little disappointed, I felt instead of the unnecessary fashion show, which feels like a Aarong adv. the sound of the Tati machine could’ve been focused and incorporated more! Also the part where Jaya Ahsan comes and sings was completely unnecessary. She isn’t a singer. Why is she here ? We have a habit of mixing everything, where we should rather stay true to few things and let them flourish. And the Gonjer Ali’s part should’ve been emphasized more and he should’ve given more space in the music video! When Culture is represented, it should be done right and with more honesty.
